Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:29.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:37.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:43.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:51.42,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:01:00.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.14,0:01:05.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.47,0:01:10.35,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:16.28,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:21.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由海底怪物所造成的 离奇船难接连发生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,象征科学文明的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.39,0:01:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,巴黎万国博览会 也在此时举行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,热爱发明的少年『强』在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,认识了小狮子『大王』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及马戏团少女『娜蒂亚』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她拥有神秘宝石『蔚蓝之水』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,企图夺取宝石的 坏蛋三人组
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然一度将娜蒂亚掳走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸好有强大显身手 才得以将她平安救出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无法再回到马戏团的 娜蒂亚与大王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟强一同前往勒阿弗尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚的『蔚蓝之水』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,究竟隐藏着什么样的秘密呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.49,0:02:11.25,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#02 小小逃亡者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 到这里应该就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些家伙应该死心了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打起精神来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到了勒阿弗尔之后 我姑姑一定会愿意帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快给我追上那两个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再拖拖拉拉下去的话 太阳就要下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被那样的小孩子 耍得团团转还像话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 要是能飞上天…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是真能飞上天的话 你打算去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想回到我出生的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你出生的国家是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不记得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王说是非洲 不知为何 我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 非洲好远
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且又好辽阔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王也想回非洲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非洲啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好远喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 整艘都是用铁打造的船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 总觉得在哪里看过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能在天上飞又能在水上航行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害的车子喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别说这些了 得快逃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 要被追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对方似乎发现我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在才发现已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎全开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,逮到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,捉迷藏到此为止 死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然这样 我就使出最后手段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后部分离！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,水中翼船绿宝石二世出动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经和他们拉开20公里远了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,靠这对翅膀能抬起船身 减少和水的摩擦力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是能跑这么快的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害喔 强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是个大发明耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个点子是个 跟我一样的法国人想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是稍微改良了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不敢相信像你这样的小孩 竟然能制作出这种船只
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我对于机械还满有自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 你真是个业余木匠的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该有更好听的说法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个装置还无法承受连续运转
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以现在怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是耍人的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不该佩服你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那也是你的发明吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 手电筒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要自己转动马达发电
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有点辛苦就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的…好像很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里就是我姑姑家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么 是强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我回来了 姑姑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欢迎回家 只有你一个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姑丈要在巴黎多留几天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正一定又是玩疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就没看他那么认真工作过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个…姑姑 我有件事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可不可以让一个女孩 在你家住一阵子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？她是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们是在巴黎认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为有坏人要抓她 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强·洛克·拉帝格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你竟然想留 一个陌生女孩住下来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她是黑人的小孩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且还带了只丑猫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本不知道他们会搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚不是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 你被那女孩骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听好了 强 趁这个机会我要跟你说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难不成要将哥哥留下来的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全都拿去买那堆破铜烂铁吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我并没有那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老是把钱花在一件件 没用的发明上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次没问题的 我有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就为了制造 根本飞不起来的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然把整座山都卖掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你脑子已经不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且这回你竟然打算 照顾那个女孩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们已经没剩多少钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还得让你去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要我照顾一个完全不认识的 黑人女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有那么大只的猫 我才不干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉了 姑姑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会再来的 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等 强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你先别走 强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫你别走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 算了 你还是别管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先别走嘛 你是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不能再给你添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说什么麻烦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才没那种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然这样 就到我家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然远了点 不过 只有我一个人住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着顾虑其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马上就到了 累了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这条路怎么这么长 又这么笔直？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以后这可以当作跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跑道？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是给飞机跑的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是谁的墓？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,塞纳星辰号一世到六世的墓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至今都未能成功飞上天的 飞机们的铁制墓碑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到了 就是那栋房子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好奇怪的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我引以为傲的家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早安 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她回去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早安 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你起得真早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好惊人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你一个人住在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 我爸是个船员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,几乎都不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 他有在姑丈那里 寄放一笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁也不晓得出海会发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他为了怕自己哪天出事 所以帮我想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是个好爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 也因为这样 我才能跟姑丈一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做自己喜欢的发明与研究
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这些全都是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 其中也有失败的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 总有一天我要制作出 能够翱翔全世界的大飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我要开它去找我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找你爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我爸他一年前 在大西洋上失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连船一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那他是被海里的怪物给…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且又没有证据说 船一定是沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的对 他一定还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我爸是世界第一的船员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他一定还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会动的楼梯是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在万国博览会上有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惜这被人给抢先发明了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让你看看我的大发明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就在上面的研究室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来是载不动两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌 真是耍人的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不该佩服你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是你做的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 可以飞上天的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飞机本来不就是在天上飞的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真正能飞上天的飞机 还没做出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对喔 最后变成了6个十字架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这东西世界上都还没出现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,塞纳星辰号八世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怪了 七世呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨天掉入塞纳河了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没关系 是为了要救你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次你们可别再让人给跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,改为陆上模式 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直立模式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你怎么了？ 从刚才就一直待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你体重多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的体重啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真没礼貌 竟然问女生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没你重啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那应该就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:18:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会遵守约定 带你飞上天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们一起飞到非洲去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这回又是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孩子们 你们逃不掉啰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乖乖将『蔚蓝之水』交出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然就得吃苦头啰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这回我可是来真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,躲起来也没用 你们就乖乖认命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森 稍微吓吓他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森 炮击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就瞄准这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们开这个逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然真的发射了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正我本来就打算 等姑丈回来就试飞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想从那种地方开溜 也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托你了 塞纳星辰号八世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两个人一起搭乘 真的没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,理论上没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 你们想用那东西做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不是要你们别白费工夫了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本就飞不起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必须加速制造升力 不然飞机是飞不起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是它从刚才 就只是在路上跑而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是怪了 这种长度应该够的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会撞上的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别再挣扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我在那里停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再不停下来 我就要直接轰了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听到没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会炸它个七零八落的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飞啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森 我有说要开火吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,飞…飞起来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那两个孩子真是惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽是敌人却令人佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在不是说这种话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森 韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快追上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,往上飞啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了 成功了 飞起来了 它飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我估计的一样 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看 真的飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 我们真的在空中飞耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然了 我的理论是完美无缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.67,0:21:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的是发明的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样直接飞到非洲去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 可以的话 沿着海岸飞会比较保险
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.64,0:22:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不晓得 不过 状况似乎不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.18,0:22:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又来了？ 不能想想办法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我从刚才就一直在努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的发明真的很会耍人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不该佩服你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:22:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 到不了非洲了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是行不通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.33,0:23:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可以在海上浮多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.73,0:23:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它能浮到有人来救我们为止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.83,0:23:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它可是彻底防水的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.17,0:23:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这回可不会再被水弄湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 看来得被雨淋了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:53.88,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.96,0:24:02.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:07.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.37,0:24:11.57,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.64,0:24:20.55,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.62,0:24:30.58,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.66,0:24:39.33,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.40,0:24:43.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.68,0:24:48.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.28,0:24:57.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.47,0:25:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 怎么你的发明 老是失败连连？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.77,0:25:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,坠落到海上的我们 被美国的新型战舰救起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.61,0:25:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行了 只能投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.94,0:25:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,邪恶三人组被捕 好不容易能松一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.18,0:25:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是神秘大海兽却出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.35,0:25:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『神秘大海兽』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.32,0:25:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见了
